          <span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background:#f0ede6;border:1px solid #ddd;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#666;flex-shrink:0;">4</span>
          活动体验
        </h2>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px;" id="bbc-act-list"></div>
        <div style="height:1px;background:#eee;margin:14px 0;"></div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:#555;margin-bottom:6px;">中高档 Spa / 按摩（每人每小时 $30～$100）</div>
