        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;font-size:14px;color:#666;">
          <span>粗估 $20 × 旅游天数</span>
          <span id="bbc-tips-p" style="font-weight:600;color:#1a1a1a;">$100</span>
        </div>
